00:59:42,210 --> 00:59:44,556
事实并非如此
But it wasn't.

520
00:59:44,588 --> 00:59:46,464
大自然的确致命 
Nature can be lethal.

521
00:59:47,716 --> 00:59:50,385
但杀伤力仍小于人类
But it doesn't hold a candle to man.

522
00:59:53,054 --> 00:59:57,851
你们都已经知道 事态的恶化有多快
You've seen how bad things can get and how quick they can get that way.

523
00:59:57,851 --> 01:00:00,604
但情况还可能雪上加霜
Well, they can get a whole lot worse.

524
01:00:00,604 --> 01:00:04,900
我们不要再争执不休了
So we're not going to fight anymore!

525
01:00:05,317 --> 01:00:09,613
我们要团结起来 想办法离开这里
We're going to pull together and find a way to get out of here!

526
01:00:11,072 --> 01:00:13,533
第一步就是封住这座池子
First, we're going to seal off this pool!

527
01:00:28,590 --> 01:00:30,175
我的天啊
Oh, my God.

528
01:00:41,102 --> 01:00:42,687
鲨鱼把他吃了
It just ate him.

529
01:00:43,605 --> 01:00:45,482
鲨鱼把他吃了
It just ate him. Christ!

530
01:00:46,858 --> 01:00:48,485
我不要走
I'm not moving.

531
01:00:48,818 --> 01:00:51,029
我要留在这里 会有人来救我们的
I'm not moving. Someone will come.

532
01:00:51,029 --> 01:00:54,334
有人会找到我们 我们不会有事的
They'll come and they'll get us, and we'll be fine.

533
01:00:54,407 --> 01:00:57,317
不，我不要走
No. I'm not moving.

534
01:00:57,536 --> 01:01:02,082
听我说，汤姆 实验室受压的临界点为何？
Listen, Tom, what is the precise structural failure limit for Aquatica?

535
01:01:02,916 --> 01:01:04,084
三千两百吨
3,200 tons.

536
01:01:04,084 --> 01:01:08,338
如果涌入的水 超过三千两百吨会怎样？
What happens when we get more than 3,200 tons of water in this rig?

537
01:01:11,758 --> 01:01:16,096
最先倒塌的是大梁 它们只能承受七吨
The support struts go first. Their tolerance is about seven tons.

538
01:01:16,346 --> 01:01:18,473
所以它们会像牙签一样折断
They'll crack like toothpicks.

539
01:01:18,473 --> 01:01:22,227
接下来墙会变型 它们只能承受十吨的压力
The walls will buckle. They can't handle more than 10 tons of pressure.

540
01:01:29,693 --> 01:01:31,570
你想留下来亲眼目睹吗？
You want to be here for that?

541
01:01:39,119 --> 01:01:40,412
才怪
Hell, no.

542
01:01:44,749 --> 01:01:47,169
真相就要揭晓了
The moment of truth. Again.

543
01:02:02,726 --> 01:02:04,477
快走…
Go! Go! Go!

544
01:02:50,909 --> 01:02:52,223
史考


545
01:02:58,240 --> 01:02:59,407
抓住你了
I got you.

546
01:03:04,955 --> 01:03:06,623
电梯烧起来了
It's burning!

547
01:03:14,256 --> 01:03:15,924
上面被电梯挡死了
The elevator's blocking the top.

548
01:03:15,924 --> 01:03:19,511
如果能够爬到第一层 我们可以改走楼梯
If we make it to Level 1, we can take the stairs out.

549
01:03:55,255 --> 01:03:56,715
我们快离开这儿吧
Let's get out of here!

550
01:03:56,715 --> 01:03:58,466
快走…
Go! Go!

551
01:04:01,803 --> 01:04:03,346
你在做什么？
What are you doing?

552
01:04:03,346 --> 01:04:06,600
如果鲨鱼破门而入的话 会随着水冲到我们身边
If they break through, water will bring them right to us.

553
01:04:06,600 --> 01:04:09,167
第二层还没有完全被淹没 如果我能打开通往第二层的门
Level 2 is only partially flooded. If I can get that door open...

554
01:04:09,217 --> 01:04:13,481
水会流到第二层去 可以为我们争取点时间
...the water will run off there,buy us some time.

555
01:04:16,234 --> 01:04:18,236
你真了不起
Big, real big.

556
01:04:18,528 --> 01:04:21,823
怎么说？ 你真有种
-What's that? -The size of your brass balls.

557
01:04:22,324 --> 01:04:23,825
小心点
Be careful.

558
01:04:33,376 --> 01:04:34,461
快走
Go!

559
01:04:40,425 --> 01:04:42,177
快走…


560
01:05:35,126 --> 01:05:37,201
卡特…


561
01:06:04,718 --> 01:06:06,323
詹妮丝


562
01:06:15,687 --> 01:06:17,147
詹妮丝，不要动
Jan, stay there!

563
01:06:23,716 --> 01:06:25,063
卡特…


564
01:06:25,113 --> 01:06:28,450
快把我拉出来 卡特，我不想死
Get me out of here, Carter! I don't want to die!

565
01:06:28,450 --> 01:06:30,577
抓住我的手
Grab my hand! Come on!

566
01:06:32,204 --> 01:06:33,538
我抓不到
I can't!

567
01:06:33,830 --> 01:06:35,165
我抓不到你的手
I can't reach!

568
01:06:37,876 --> 01:06:39,586
快抓住我的手
-Take it! -I can't reach!

569
01:07:25,069 --> 01:07:27,175
史考 什么事？


570
01:07:27,801 --> 01:07:29,970
你开得到上面那扇门吗？
Can you reach that door above you?

571
01:07:33,849 --> 01:07:35,183
太高了
It's too high.

572
01:07:36,393 --> 01:07:38,270
太高了
It's too high.

573
01:08:00,083 --> 01:08:02,419
鲨鱼说不定已经游到那层去了
Sharks probably flooded that level too.

574
01:08:35,493 --> 01:08:38,538
还好你们到这边来了 另外一半已经被淹没了
Good thing you came to this side. The other side's underwater.

575
01:08:38,538 --> 01:08:41,491
那只是巧合 我们只是误打误撞
-We didn't exactly plan it. -Yeah, it wasn't planned.

576
01:08:41,541 --> 01:08:43,627
只剩下你们了？
Are you all that made it?

577
01:08:50,467 --> 01:08:55,130
我们终于到了第一层 我们现在可以改走楼梯到顶层
We did it. We're on Level 1. We can take the stairs to the surface.

578
01:08:55,180 --> 01:08:57,549
楼梯全被淹没了，相信我
The stairs are flooded. Trust me, I know.

579
01:08:57,599 --> 01:08:58,892
你确定？
Are you sure?

580
01:09:00,393 --> 01:09:02,979
上帝，别再折磨我们了
Give us a goddamn break, can't You?

581
01:09:14,574 --> 01:09:16,159
它总是有求必应 
He always answers.

582
01:09:17,202 --> 01:09:20,372
只是未必如你的愿
Sometimes, the answer you get isn't the answer you want.

583
01:09:24,876 --> 01:09:27,170
我们离顶层只有60尺了
We're 60 feet from the surface.

584
01:09:27,963 --> 01:09:31,424
这层有紧急逃生门，对吧？
There's an emergency hatch on this level, right?

585
01:09:31,967 --> 01:09:34,511
这一层有防止积水用的 紧急抽水机
This level has bilge pumps on it for storm runoff.

586
01:09:34,511 --> 01:09:38,765
如果能够启动紧急发电机的话 可以抽干楼梯的水
If we re-route the emergency generators, we could drain a stairway.

587
01:09:39,850 --> 01:09:41,101
你确定吗？
You sure?

588
01:09:41,351 --> 01:09:42,978
你能信任谁？
Who you going to trust?

589
01:09:46,565 --> 01:09:48,191
你 没错
-You. -That's right.

590
01:09:48,191 --> 01:09:49,860
你要信任我
You trust me.

591
01:09:59,411 --> 01:10:02,111
本来讲好明晚要在这里打牌
We had poker here tomorrow night.

592
01:10:02,289 --> 01:10:05,917
她拿到一对的时候 总是会冒险一博
She'd always draw to the inside straight when she could've stuck with a pair.

593
01:10:05,917 --> 01:10:07,502
她总是满怀梦想
Big dreams.

594
01:10:14,676 --> 01:10:17,512
就算死到临头 也不能降低自己的标准
Even in death: Standards.

595
01:10:19,514 --> 01:10:23,768
詹妮丝是个正常的女人 她屋里一定有用电池的东西
Jan was a healthy girl. Something in here has to run on batteries.

596
01:10:24,728 --> 01:10:29,808
说的好 你们女人会把… 那玩意儿藏在哪里？
-Nice. -Where would a girl keep her... ...thing?

597
01:10:29,858 --> 01:10:31,818
你是怎么回事？
What's the matter with you?

598
01:10:39,284 --> 01:10:41,661
我的皮肤开始出血了
My skin's starting to hemorrhage.

599
01:10:42,078 --> 01:10:44,414
鲨鱼闻到血腥味的话… 
The sharks smell the blood.

600
01:10:45,790 --> 01:10:47,292
这样可以把伤口盖住
This'll coat it with oil.

601
01:10:47,292 --> 01:10:49,972
卡特，你在下面说的话…
Look, Carter, what you said down there...

602
01:10:51,421 --> 01:10:53,256
也许你是对的
...maybe you were right.

603
01:10:54,758 --> 01:10:56,635
我做的一切
Everything I've done...

604
01:10:58,720 --> 01:11:01,431
没有你都不可能成功
...I don't think I could've done it without you.

605
01:11:02,015 --> 01:11:05,769
苏珊，问题就出在这里
I know, Susan. That's the problem.

606
01:11:08,146 --> 01:11:09,606
已经四点了
Four a.m.

607
01:11:10,190 --> 01:11:13,818
我明白，真是度日如年啊
I know. One night feels like a whole week.

608
01:11:14,945 --> 01:11:16,279
相对论
Relativity.

609
01:11:16,780 --> 01:11:18,198
你这话什么意思？
What do you mean?

610
01:11:18,198 --> 01:11:20,617
爱因斯坦的相对论
Einstein's theory of relativity.

611
01:11:21,201 --> 01:11:24,704
抓着烧红的铁板时 一秒比一小时还漫长
Grab hold of a hot pan, a second can seem like an hour.

612
01:11:25,163 --> 01:11:30,043
但搂着美女时 一小时比一秒还快
Put your hands on a hot woman... ...an hour can seem like a second.

613
01:11:30,043 --> 01:11:32,504
一切都是相对的
It's all relative.

614
01:11:35,966 --> 01:11:40,595
我在加州理工念了四年 但这是我所听过最精辟的解释
I spent four years at Cal Tech. That's the best physics explanation I've heard.

615
01:11:43,640 --> 01:11:44,933
可以用
It works.

616
01:11:46,560 --> 01:11:48,311
你留下来陪博士
You stay with the doc.

617
01:11:48,311 --> 01:11:53,149
我和史考想办法到实验室去 抽干楼梯间的水
Me and Scoggs are going to try to get to the wet lab... ...drain that stairwell.

618
01:11:56,862 --> 01:11:58,655
神父… 干嘛？
-Preach? -What?

619
01:12:00,782 --> 01:12:02,951
帮我拉拉链
Would you zip me up, please?

620
01:12:34,399 --> 01:12:36,985
我们杀了一只 还剩下两只鲨鱼
We got one, there's two sharks left...

621
01:12:36,985 --> 01:12:40,355
你居然还在浴室 和博士互吐爱意
...and you and the doc are doing a little bathroom love.

622
01:12:40,405 --> 01:12:43,158
你的毛病有没有药医？
They got a pill for what's wrong with you?

623
01:12:53,752 --> 01:12:57,018
我要到我房里去拿研究资料
I need to get some things from my quarters. Research data.

624
01:12:57,068 --> 01:13:00,050
那些实验真的成功了
The tests, they worked.

625
01:13:00,842 --> 01:13:04,804
已经死了这么多人 别再为你的研究数据害人了
So much death around us, to risk any more life for some numbers....

626
01:13:06,681 --> 01:13:10,865
若我不拿那些资料 他们就都白死了
Without that data, everyone dying isn't just tragic, it's useless.

627
01:13:10,915 --> 01:13:14,658
博士，死亡一向很枉然
Death is always useless, Doctor.

628
01:13:24,991 --> 01:13:26,493
就是这里了
This is it.

629
01:13:32,207 --> 01:13:34,292
你留在这里，我马上回来
Stay here. I'll be back before you know it.

630
01:13:36,753 --> 01:13:38,818
卡特…


631
01:14:45,572 --> 01:14:47,073
发生什么事了？
What's going on?

632
01:14:47,532 --> 01:14:49,659
那是什么鬼东西
What the hell's going on? What is that?

633
01:14:49,659 --> 01:14:51,361
没事的
It's okay!

634
01:14:51,411 --> 01:14:53,488
你叫什么？ 我们没事的
-What is that? -We're all right!

635
01:14:53,538 --> 01:14:56,124
搞什么鬼？ 没事了
-What the fuck? -It's okay.

636
01:14:57,991 --> 01:14:59,346
没事了…


637
01:14:59,669 --> 01:15:02,047
你不是要回来找我吗？
I thought you were coming back for me.

638
01:15:02,339 --> 01:15:05,300
控制面板被监视器挡住了
One of your monitors is blocking the panel.

639
01:15:05,300 --> 01:15:07,594
来帮我推一下吧
You want to help me move it?

640
01:15:07,594 --> 01:15:10,858
我看我们还是一起行动吧
I say we do everything right together.

641
01:15:11,973 --> 01:15:13,058
一起行动
Right together.

642
01:15:27,572 --> 01:15:28,406

Hello.

643
01:15:29,866 --> 01:15:32,202
我叫做雪曼杜德利
My name is Sherman Dudley...

644
01:15:32,827 --> 01:15:37,760
如果你看到这卷带子的话 表示我已经死了 以下是我的遗言
...and if this message finds you, I did not survive, so this is my legacy.

645
01:15:37,874 --> 01:15:41,378
这辈子我最爱的两件事 第一是传道，第二是喝酒
I have loved the pulpit and I have loved the bottle.

646
01:15:42,295 --> 01:15:46,101
我努力想做个好丈夫，好爸爸
I did my best to be a good husband, a father.

647
01:15:46,925 --> 01:15:48,760
但都没有成功
I came up wanting.

648
01:15:49,845 --> 01:15:52,222
我还有什么好说的呢
So what do I have to say to you?

649
01:15:53,598 --> 01:15:56,101
我又留下些什么？
What mark do I have to leave behind?

650
01:16:02,107 --> 01:16:05,527
首先介绍蛋卷的做法 一次打两个蛋，不是三个
We'll begin with the perfect omelet, made with two eggs, not three.

651
01:16:05,527 --> 01:16:08,791
那些菜鸟常常会加牛奶 增加浓度，真是大错特错
Amateurs often add milk for density. This is a mistake.

652
01:18:43,602 --> 01:18:45,854
卡特，快来
Come on!

653
01:19:18,512 --> 01:19:20,388

I got you. Come on.

654
01:19:34,236 --> 01:19:35,904
你真讨厌，史考
Damn you, Scoggs.

655
01:19:46,831 --> 01:19:48,333
苏珊呢？
Where's Susan?

656
01:19:50,961 --> 01:19:52,003
我惨了，
I'm done.

657
01:19:52,003 --> 01:19:55,715
咱们黑人 碰到这种情况就死定了
Brothers never make it out of situations like this. Not ever!

658
01:23:49,074 --> 01:23:54,381
苏珊…


659
01:23:57,666 --> 01:24:01,221
你们成功了吗，史考呢？
Did you do it? Where's Scoggins?

660
01:24:03,713 --> 01:24:06,500
我不想打断你们
I hate to interrupt this moment of burgeoning intimacy...

661
01:24:06,550 --> 01:24:08,468
我们可不可以 快点离开这里啊？
...but can we get the fuck out of here?

662
01:24:19,521 --> 01:24:21,481
这是唯一的出路？
-Is this the only way? -Exits are flooded.

663
01:24:21,481 --> 01:24:25,151
出口都已经被淹没了 整个实验室都在下沉 不这样就出不去了
Whole place is sinking. It's this way or no way at all.

664
01:24:26,111 --> 01:24:28,730
你有好消息的话就现在说吧
You can bring on the good news anytime now.

665
01:24:28,780 --> 01:24:32,692
鲨鱼会受到混浊的水 及鲜明的颜色所吸引
Sharks are attracted to churning water, bright colors.

666
01:24:32,742 --> 01:24:35,526
这些灭火器 可以让它们暂时分心
These extinguishers will be a distraction.

667
01:24:36,663 --> 01:24:38,123
我们怎么办？
What about us?

668
01:24:38,123 --> 01:24:42,335
我们穿上救生衣 浮出水面速度过快肺脏会爆的
The vest'll bring you up too fast. Your lungs'll pop like a balloon.

669
01:24:43,336 --> 01:24:45,372
你一定不是班上最快乐的小孩
You weren't the sunny kid in your class.

670
01:24:45,422 --> 01:24:47,768
我从来没有上过学
I never went to class.

671
01:24:48,383 --> 01:24:50,836
我们离水面有多远？ 60英尺？
How far to the surface? Sixty feet?

672
01:24:50,886 --> 01:24:56,579
没什么大不了的 上升的时候吐气尽快离开水面
There's nothing to it. Exhale on the way up, and get the hell out of the water.

673
01:24:56,975 --> 01:25:00,739
我在打开气密锁之前 得先平衡压力
I got to equalize the pressure before we blow the air lock.

674
01:25:01,313 --> 01:25:07,538
我要让水淹没这个房间 几秒钟之内就完成了
I got to let the room fill up with water. It'll only take a few seconds.

675
01:25:07,944 --> 01:25:09,842
准备好了吗？
You ready?

676
01:25:10,572 --> 01:25:11,615

No.

677
01:25:12,574 --> 01:25:13,804
准备好才怪
Not in the least.

678
01:25:32,719 --> 01:25:38,675
我行经死亡之谷，不畏惧恶魔 因为有你与我同在
''Though I walk through the valley of the shadow of death... ''...I shall fear no evil... ''...for Thou art with me...

679
01:25:38,725 --> 01:25:46,527
汝之权杖给我慰藉 汝之慈悲，恩慈将长伴我左右
''...Thy rod and Thy staff, they comfort me. ''Surely goodness and mercy shall follow me all the days of my life... ''

680
01:25:46,577 --> 01:25:47,893
因为我带着一根大棍子
...because I carry a big stick...

681
01:25:47,943 --> 01:25:50,604
而且是死亡谷中 最可怕的凶神恶煞
...and I'm the meanest motherfucker in the valley.

682
01:25:50,654 --> 01:25:53,899
我们杀了两只 还剩一只要解决
Two sharks down, Lord. One demon fish to go.

683
01:25:53,949 --> 01:25:55,442
跟我一起说，阿门
Can I get an ''amen''?

684
01:25:55,492 --> 01:25:56,409
阿门
Amen!

685
01:25:56,409 --> 01:25:58,518
我听不到 阿门
-I can't hear you! -Amen!

686
01:25:58,568 --> 01:26:00,259
大声一点
Give me an ''amen''!

687
01:26:00,309 --> 01:26:04,042
保佑我们吧
-Stay with us, Lord! -Amen.

688
01:26:06,253 --> 01:26:08,789
我数到三，准备好了吗？
Okay, hold on three! Ready?

689
01:26:08,839 --> 01:26:11,925
一，二，三
One! Two! Three!

690
01:27:47,103 --> 01:27:48,855
快游
Swim!

691
01:28:26,393 --> 01:28:28,603
我的天啊
Oh, my God!

692
01:29:05,599 --> 01:29:08,310
它们简直是恶魔
It's the devil, you know.

693
01:29:18,862 --> 01:29:22,053
只要我们能离开这儿 他就不会有事的
He'll be okay if we can get out of here.

694
01:29:33,627 --> 01:29:35,495
真该死
Son of a bitch.

695
01:29:35,545 --> 01:29:36,546

What?

696
01:29:36,546 --> 01:29:41,238
怎么了？ 篱笆在水底的部份是钛合金 但在水面上只有钢丝
Those fences are titanium underneath, but on top, they're just plain steel.

697
01:29:43,512 --> 01:29:49,424
是它们把我们赶到这儿来的 利用我们淹没实验室
They've been herding us, pushing us where they want. Using us to flood the facility.

698
01:29:51,186 --> 01:29:53,513
我的天啊
Oh, my God.

699
01:29:53,563 --> 01:29:55,307
那就是谜语的答案
That's the answer to the riddle.

700
01:29:55,357 --> 01:29:59,163
因为这就是那些 八千磅的巨鲨打的主意
Because that's what an 8,000-pound mako thinks about.

701
01:29:59,694 --> 01:30:02,280
它们梦想自由
About freedom.

702
01:30:03,156 --> 01:30:05,940
梦想一片蔚蓝大海
About the deep blue sea.

703
01:30:08,245 --> 01:30:10,799
我们一定要杀了它
We have to kill her.

704
01:30:12,332 --> 01:30:16,190
你终于上道了
That's the first real smart thing you've said all day.

705
01:30:20,298 --> 01:30:22,227
我们动手吧
Here we go.

706
01:30:39,067 --> 01:30:40,840
走吧
Let's go.

707
01:30:51,037 --> 01:30:54,791
这些信号弹里的火药应该够了
We ought to get 2.5 sticks of dynamite out of these flares.

708
01:31:00,338 --> 01:31:02,958
你从这上面应该可以看到 我是否射中它
From up here, you ought to be able to see me spear it.

709
01:31:03,008 --> 01:31:08,630
我一射中它，你就将缆线的 这一头接到电池上
When I do, you take this end of this cable... ...hook it up to the positive side of the boat battery.

710
01:31:08,680 --> 01:31:11,068
炸得它粉身碎骨
And boom!

711
01:31:46,968 --> 01:31:49,421
该死，我射不中它
Damn! I can't get her!

712
01:31:49,471 --> 01:31:51,911
太远了
She's too far away!

713
01:31:53,141 --> 01:31:55,508
我知道如何诱它过来
I know how to get her.

714
01:31:55,560 --> 01:31:57,479
怎么做？
How?

715
01:31:58,104 --> 01:32:01,149
以身做饵 什么？
Bait.

716
01:32:13,537 --> 01:32:16,164
它也许是世上最聪明的动物
She may be the smartest animal in the world...

717
01:32:16,164 --> 01:32:18,792
不过终归还是动物
...but she's still just an animal.

718
01:32:20,335 --> 01:32:22,379
过来吧
Come to Mama.

719
01:32:35,684 --> 01:32:44,401
苏珊，不要…
No! Susan, don't!

720
01:32:58,832 --> 01:33:01,001
快到岸上来
Get out of the water!

721
01:34:55,031 --> 01:34:56,483
好了，上帝…
All right, Lord....

722
01:34:56,533 --> 01:34:58,235
快开枪
Shoot it, Preach!

723
01:34:58,285 --> 01:34:59,945
这是为了史考报仇
This is for Scoggins.

724
01:34:59,995 --> 01:35:01,819
开枪
Shoot it!

725
01:35:08,295 --> 01:35:09,546
该死的
Damn!

726
01:35:15,051 --> 01:35:17,345
快炸了它
Blow it, Preach! Blow it!

727
01:35:17,762 --> 01:35:20,859
快接上电池，把它炸了
The battery! Blow it!

728
01:35:24,603 --> 01:35:26,281
快点
Do it!

729
01:35:53,246 --> 01:35:54,414
该死


730
01:36:24,016 --> 01:36:25,403
卡特


731
01:36:28,375 --> 01:36:31,023
帮我带点生鱼片上来
Bring me some sushi!

732
01:36:55,235 --> 01:36:59,135
这么大的目标你居然还打中我
Forty-five-foot shark... ...and you hit me.

733
01:36:59,155 --> 01:37:01,107
真是神准
Nice.

734
01:37:01,157 --> 01:37:04,515
你让高兴我没让它一口吃了你
Could've been worse. I could've let him eat your ass.

735
01:37:11,585 --> 01:37:13,983
卡特，实验室在下沉，对吧？
Carter, we're sinking, right?

736
01:37:14,212 --> 01:37:16,256
没错
Yeah.

737
01:37:16,256 --> 01:37:18,425
我问你一件事
Let me ask you something.

738
01:37:19,718 --> 01:37:22,345
你确定只有三条巨鲨吗？
Are you sure it was just three sharks?

739
01:37:22,554 --> 01:37:24,545
对
Yeah.

740
01:37:25,119 --> 01:37:26,276
好吧


741
01:37:33,940 --> 01:37:36,057
这还差不多
That's more like it.

742
01:37:43,950 --> 01:37:46,161
接班人员来了
Here comes the next shift.

743
01:37:46,995 --> 01:37:51,187
告诉你，我不干了
Let me tell you, man... ...I quit this job.

744
01:37:54,961 --> 01:37:57,641
我宁愿回贫民窟去
Take me back to the ghetto.

745
01:37:57,797 --> 01:37:59,664
